01:06:43,571 --> 01:06:45,239
Bagus, simpan saja
itu stabil, Peter.

1292
01:06:45,272 --> 01:06:46,240
Menyalin.

1293
01:06:46,273 --> 01:06:47,007
Dimana Josh dan Sophie?

