Tsunami melanda
Lokasi Josh dan Sophie.

1314
01:08:29,777 --> 01:08:30,745
Aku akan memeriksanya.

1315
01:08:46,293 --> 01:08:47,528
Sophie, ambil walkie-talkie.

1316
01:08:52,734 --> 01:08:54,836
Josh, Sophie, 
